  "description": "GMunchies is a modern vending solutions brand focused on delivering convenient, high-quality snacks, drinks, and coffee through smart, reliable machines. Built for schools, offices, and public spaces, GMunchies combines clean design, cashless technology, and fast service to create a smooth everyday experience. The brand focuses on accessibility, efficiency, and making quick breaks better for everyone.",
  "mission": "To provide easy access to fresh snacks, drinks, and coffee through well-designed vending machines that fit naturally into everyday environments. GMunchies aims to improve convenience while keeping service fast, simple, and dependable.",
  "vision": "To become a trusted vending brand known for smart technology, clean design, and consistent service across multiple locations. GMunchies aims to grow into a recognizable name that people rely on for quick, quality refreshment wherever they are.",
